EventDescription.SourceString: The Darkwood Vale is a mysterious place. A dense and impermeable jungle envelops a massive swath of dead land where nothing has grown in ages. It is said that ages ago the gods gashed the lush terrain as punishment for the sins of the Old Ones. Strange and ancient forces seem to linger. Journey into the Darkwood and witness its ominous reality for yourself. Complete levels for rewards.
